Linux-shell over a network:
1. server.cpp and server.hpp 
     - server class implementation. 
     - creates, bind and listen socket and maintains communication with the client

2. client.cpp and client.hpp 
     - client class implementation. 
     - creates socket and connects it to the server and maintains communication with the server 

3. Makefile
     - make: automatic building your code with cpp
     - make clean: clean compiled files